\end_layout

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
is called 
\begin_inset Formula $\textbf{exact}$
\end_inset

 
\series bold
at
\series default
 
\begin_inset Formula $M$
\end_inset

 if 
\begin_inset Formula $\mathrm{im}\,\varphi=\ker\psi$
\end_inset

.
 A 
\begin_inset Formula $\textbf{short exact sequence}$
\end_inset

 is a sequence of 
\begin_inset Formula $R$
\end_inset

-modules and 
\begin_inset Formula $R$
\end_inset

-linear maps
\end_layout

