end{tikzcd}
\backslash
end{equation}
\end_layout

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
Moreover, if 
\begin_inset Formula $\varphi_{1}$
\end_inset

 is injective, then 
\begin_inset Formula $\widetilde{\varphi_{1}}$
\end_inset

 is injective; and if 
\begin_inset Formula $\varphi_{2}'$
\end_inset

 is surjective, then 
\begin_inset Formula $\overline{\varphi_{2}'}$
\end_inset

 is surjective.
 
\begin_inset ERT
status open

\begin_layout Plain Layout


\backslash
end{prop}
\end_layout

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
\begin_inset ERT
status open

\begin_layout Plain Layout


\backslash
begin{proof}
\end_layout

\end_inset

 
\begin_inset ERT
