begin{lemma}
\backslash
label{lemma}
\end_layout

\end_inset

 Let 
\begin_inset Formula $A$
\end_inset

 be a ring, 
\begin_inset Formula $M_{i}\subset E_{i}$
\end_inset

 for all 
\begin_inset Formula $i\in I$
\end_inset

 be 
\begin_inset Formula $A$
\end_inset

-modules over 
\begin_inset Formula $A$
\end_inset

.
 Then 
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\bigoplus_{i\in I}M_{i}\subset_{e}\bigoplus_{i\in I}E_{i}\quad\text{if and only if}\quad M_{i}\subset_{e}E_{i}
\]

\end_inset

for all 
\begin_inset Formula $i\in I$
\end_inset

.
\begin_inset ERT
status open

\begin_layout Plain Layout


\backslash
