begin{lemma}
\backslash
label{lemma}
\end_layout

\end_inset

 Let 
\begin_inset Formula $A$
\end_inset

 be a ring and let 
\begin_inset Formula $M_{1},\dots,M_{n}$
\end_inset

 be 
\begin_inset Formula $A$
\end_inset

-modules.
 Then 
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
E\left(\bigoplus_{i=1}^{n}M_{i}\right)=\bigoplus_{i=1}^{n}E\left(M_{i}\right).
\]

\end_inset


\begin_inset ERT
