\end_layout

\end_inset

 tells us that 
\begin_inset Formula $k$
\end_inset

 is an essential extension of 
\begin_inset Formula $A/\mathfrak{p}$
\end_inset

, so 
\begin_inset Formula $E$
\end_inset

 contains a copy of 
\begin_inset Formula $k$
\end_inset

